<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Banned</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KyZXEJqJtA1+OGA4rO4Jt7KbdB4sZ4c2vFeSHRtYgSkKDFh7vLkW7W6tC9mDt9hX" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .card-header {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border-bottom: none;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .card-body {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            border-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #00408d;
            border-color: #003a7d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>Account Banned</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Your account has been banned due to violating our terms of service. If you believe this is an error, please contact support.</p>
                <p><strong>Reason: </strong>Your account violated our community guidelines.</p>
                <a href="/contact-support" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
                <br><br>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Go to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-pzjw8f+ua7Kw1TIq0p3v3Wf4FyZp5g6Q6hO1s7y3SgGzmvnk43U6s3wEmkqJb+2c" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
